net.sf.expectit

Interface MultiResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MatchResult, Result

    public interface MultiResult
extends Result
    A representation of the result of multiple match operations.

    The result of the one operation is selected by implementation to represent all the other operations and fulfill the contract of the Result super interface.

    For example, the result can represent a combination of match operations, while the match with the greatest end position is selected to implement the super interface.

    • Method Detail

      • getResults

        List<Result> getResults()
        Returns an unmodifiable list of the result instances of all the performed match operations . The list includes the result of the one operation chosen to represent the others.

        The order of the elements should correspond to the order in which the match operations have been performed. Never returns null.

        Returns:
        an unmodifiable list of all the match results
